@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.68
    v2 = wp.cos(v1)
    v2 = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = ((v0 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.53)) * ((v0 + 0.67 / v1 + 0.36) * v1))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.67 + v1 + 0.69) + 0.92) - v0)
    v0 = ((tmp - wp.exp(v2 + 0.15)) + wp.exp(0.76))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.63 * v0 + 0.91) + 0.27))
    data[tid] = v0
